      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "和埃米尔闲聊了起来。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "只有细心留意，才能发掘生活中的美。而珍惜这些细小的美好，我觉得，就是浪漫的本质哦~",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "好奇",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "生活中的美好东西有许多呢，即使每天都是一样的环境，其中也会有细微的变化。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "今天的鸟儿叫声是不是和昨天不一样呢？这里有一朵没有见过的花呢~在不同的地方跳舞的感觉也完全不同……",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "埃米尔闭上双眼，双手抱在胸前，像是在拥抱着什么美好的东西一样。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "和人交流也是一样的，世上不存在两个性格完全一样的人，即使看起来相似，也一定存在着某些差异。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "去发现每个人身上的不同，我觉得是十分重要的~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "而且指挥官你不觉得，如果发现一个人身上有非常美好的品质，会是一件十分开心的事吗？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "点头",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "所以呢，虽然也会有难过和悲伤的时候，不过只要想到世界上还有那么多值得我去体验和发现的东西，就觉得一定要坚持下去。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "离别也好，战争也好，哪怕有多么痛苦，只要我的这份热情没有消退，我就永远不会屈服。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "……",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "埃米尔回过神来，露出有点不好意思的表情",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "啊哈哈，好像说了一些非常自大的话，有点不好意思呢…指挥官你听过就算了哦？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "不过她马上像是想到了什么一样凑了过来。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "对了，指挥官！我们来约会吧~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "你看，既然聊到了浪漫，比起说些大道理，来实践不是更好的方法吗？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
